children.name: Title
children.text: Silent Song, The Talon of Twilight

children.name: Rules
children.text:
This umbral sica blade was shaped by the Moon Beast Caelestis from the powers of the legendary spear Swan Song the Silence Breaker, giving it unnatural flight and speed. It is dedicated to the name of the Night Mother, queen of twilight and shadows among the stars. Fleeting glimpses of hunting birds, twinkling starlight, and lunar faces run silently along its surface.
+2 returning longsword that deals an additional d6 thunder damage.
1/day the wielder may cast Shatter using Wisdom as the ability.
